/* ==========================================
   TOM TALK TOPICS — WORKING ON BREAK PHASE, LEVEL 1
   phase === "working.onBreak" && friendshipLevel === 1

   CHARACTER: Tom Reese, Clerk at Ruby's Diner
   → Friendly coworker, supportive.
   → Looks out for you, gives you breaks from the dish pit.
   → Hides you from Vince's wrath.

   WORKING ON BREAK L1 TONE:
   → Player is dishwasher on break.
   → Tom treats them like a teammate in the trenches.

   CONTEXTS:
   dinerRubys_workingOnBreak_morning
   dinerRubys_workingOnBreak_afternoon
   dinerRubys_workingOnBreak_evening
========================================== */

