<<dialog "charClerkTom">>Trying to.<</dialog>`,
                friendship: 2, trust: 1
            },
            {
text: `<<set _img = "assets/content/scenes/interactions/tom/level1/tomOnBreakMorning-2.webp">>
<<image _img "100%">>
<<narrative>>Tom is holding a handful of wet silverware he just pulled from the rack.<</narrative>>
<<dialog "charClerkTom">>Sorry, had to steal these directly from the drying rack. We're completely out of forks out here.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>They're burning hot.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "charClerkTom">>I know, I feel like I'm carrying coals. Thanks for washing them fast though.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>No problem.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "charClerkTom">>I owe you.<</dialog>`,
                friendship: 2, trust: 0
            },
            {
text: `<<set _img = "assets/content/scenes/interactions/tom/level1/tomOnBreakMorning-3.webp">>
<<image _img "100%">>
<<narrative>>Tom nods toward the front counter with a sympathetic look.<</narrative>>
<<dialog "charClerkTom">>I see you dealing with that mountain of grease back there. You surviving?<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>Barely.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "charClerkTom">>Take your full break. If Emma asks where you are, I'll tell her you're taking out trash.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>I appreciate the cover.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "charClerkTom">>Teammates gotta look out for each other.<</dialog>`,
                friendship: 2, trust: 1
            }
        ],

        water_break: [
            {
text: `<<set _img = "assets/content/scenes/interactions/tom/level1/tomOnBreakMorning-1.webp">>
<<image _img "100%">>
<<narrative>>Tom hands you a large plastic cup full of ice water before you even ask.<</narrative>>
<<dialog "charClerkTom">>Drink. You look like you just walked out of a sauna back there.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>The dishwasher is basically a sauna.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "charClerkTom">>I figured. Hydrate before Vince finds you sitting still.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>Good looking out.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "charClerkTom">>Gotta keep my dishwasher alive.<</dialog>`,
                friendship: 2, trust: 1
            },
            {
text: `<<set _img = "assets/content/scenes/interactions/tom/level1/tomOnBreakMorning-2.webp">>
<<image _img "100%">>
<<narrative>>Tom is wiping the ice machine with a damp towel.<</narrative>>
<<dialog "charClerkTom">>If you want a soda instead of water, just fill it in a dark cup. Vince assumes it's iced tea.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>Is that allowed?<</dialog>>
<<dialog "charClerkTom">>Allowed? No. Necessary for survival at minimum wage? Absolutely.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>I won't tell.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "charClerkTom">>Knew I could trust you.<</dialog>`,
                friendship: 2, trust: 1
            },
            {
text: `<<set _img = "assets/content/scenes/interactions/tom/level1/tomOnBreakMorning-3.webp">>
<<image _img "100%">>
<<narrative>>Tom is taking a quick sip from his own water bottle hidden under the counter.<</narrative>>
<<dialog "charClerkTom">>The heat up front is bad, but the kitchen gets brutal. Make sure you don't lock your knees standing there.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>I'm used to standing.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "charClerkTom">>Just remind yourself to stretch. I forgot my first week and I felt it for a month.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>Thanks, Tom.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "charClerkTom">>Anytime.<</dialog>`,
                friendship: 2, trust: 0
            }
        ],

        vince_alert: [
            {
text: `<<set _img = "assets/content/scenes/interactions/tom/level1/tomOnBreakMorning-1.webp">>
<<image _img "100%">>
<<narrative>>Tom kicks the side of your foot lightly under the counter to get your attention.<</narrative>>
<<dialog "charClerkTom">>Heads up, Vince is walking up and down the aisles looking for something to yell about.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>I'm just resting.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "charClerkTom">>Grab a towel anyway. If you have a towel in your hand, he thinks you're returning to work. Works every time.<</dialog>>
