<<dialog "charClerkTom">>It's sugar and aggressively strong peppermint. Wakes the brain up when you're midway through a shift.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>Good strategy.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "charClerkTom">>We do what we must.<</dialog>`,
