            {
text: `<<set _img = "assets/content/scenes/interactions/tom/level1/tomOnBreakAfternoon-3.webp">>
<<image _img "100%">>
<<narrative>>Tom is casually chewing on something small as he talks.<</narrative>>
<<dialog "charClerkTom">>Emma keeps a stash of crackers in the second drawer under the register. If you ever need one, she gave me permission to distribute.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>Really?<</dialog>>
<<dialog "charClerkTom">>Yeah. She's the diner mom. Just discreetly grab one when Vince is blind.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>I'll remember that.<</dialog>>
