            {
text: `<<set _img = "assets/content/scenes/interactions/tom/level1/tomOnBreakAfternoon-1.webp">>
<<image _img "100%">>
<<narrative>>Tom taps you on the shoulder lightly.<</narrative>>
<<dialog "charClerkTom">>Hey, you're doing great back there. Don't let James' yelling get to you, he yells at the spoons too.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>It's loud back there.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "charClerkTom">>I know. It's a warzone. But you're handling it better than the last guy did.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>What happened to him?<</dialog>>
<<dialog "charClerkTom">>He cried and walked out on a Tuesday. So, you're officially beating the record.<</dialog>`,
                friendship: 2, trust: 1
            },
            {
text: `<<set _img = "assets/content/scenes/interactions/tom/level1/tomOnBreakAfternoon-2.webp">>
<<image _img "100%">>
<<narrative>>Tom leans back against the counter, smiling supportively.<</narrative>>
<<dialog "charClerkTom">>Almost halfway through the shift. From here on out, it's a downhill slide to freedom.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>It still feels like a long time.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "charClerkTom">>Don't think about the hours. Think about the next ten minutes. Break it down. It's a mental game.<</dialog>>
